name: Security Breach
Lore: 'The Rebellion''s limited resources force it to consider the wisdom of any military encounter. In many cases, retreat or deception is a preferable recourse.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Cancels game text of [Reflections III] Naboo sites.  Unless present with 3 other characters, Derdram''s and Ephant Mon''s game texts are canceled.  Once per game, may place this Effect out of play to reduce your battle damage by 4. (Immune to Alter.)',
